Package: tweetscores
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the Estimation of Ideology Scores with Twitter Data
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2018-01-23
Author: Pablo Barbera <P.Barbera@lse.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Pablo Barbera <P.Barbera@lse.ac.uk>
Description: This package provides a series of functions to collect and analyze
    Twitter data, and to estimate the ideological positions of Twitter users with
    the method described in Barbera (2015, Political Analysis).
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R2WinBUGS
Imports:
    yaml,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    ROAuth,
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
